desc_short	-----								There’s no better disguise than looking exactly like your enemy: Dysan the shapeshifter is an upcoming PC fantasy RPG, featuring the possibility of giving its players the opportunity to shape-shift into their enemies and even into any NPC creature to get unique opportunities to win battles and solve the game.							
developer									CCG								
